        <Param val="This is a memory test.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;First, you will see two pictures of different objects one by one. Try to remember them carefully.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Then, you will hear a &quot;Ding&quot;, followed by a short description (like “a red bus”). As soon as you hear the description, try to recall the object image you just saw. You will have 4 seconds to do this. &amp;#10;&amp;#10;Finally, you will see a new image. Your task is to decide quickly if this image is one of the pictures you saw earlier. &amp;#10;&amp;#10;Press 's' if it matches (YES), press 'd' if it does not match (NO).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Press 's' when you're ready to start the practice." valType="str" updates="constant" name="text"/>
